      <td style="text-align: left">Offline and Online Players Only</td>
      <td style="text-align: left">This displays the playerâ€™s name whose level is the highest in the current world; where <span id="redType"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">x</code></span> represents the relative position of the player in terms of level. For example: for a player with the highest level, <span id="redType"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">x</code></span> would be 1; for the player with the second highest level, <span id="redType"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">x</code></span> would be 2, and so on. The name displayed is provided by <span id="redType"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">GameProfile#getName</code></span>.</td>
